{"type":"text","timestamp":1775855269371,"sessionID":"ses_286c8d4fbffe4UkAR6BFerFisn","part":{"id":"prt_d7938b14d0014zgza62EFBv3Ac","messageID":"msg_d7938a718001ZQDbo03aqeIhVS","sessionID":"ses_286c8d4fbffe4UkAR6BFerFisn","type":"text","text":"Here is the verification report for **AR-022 â€” CLI publish command** against spec:\n\n---\n\n## Test Results\n\n**160 passed, 7 failed, 1 skipped** (out of 168)\n\n### 7 Failing Tests\n\n| Test | Root Cause |\n|------|-----------|\n| `test_invalid_language_raises` | `_apply_option_overrides` doesn't trigger Pydantic validation on `model_copy(update=...)` |\n| `test_raises_value_error_for_unknown_provider` | Docker unavailable check fires before provider validation |\n| `test_raises_value_error_for_unknown_build_mode` | Pydantic error message doesn't match test regex `'Unsupported build mode'` |\n| `test_version_is_updated_in_metadata` | `_update_publish_metadata` only saves `agent_id`, `agent_endpoint`, `k8s_deployment` â€” not `version` |\n| `test_description_is_updated_in_metadata` | Same â€” `description` not saved to metadata |\n| `test_region_is_updated_in_metadata` | Same â€” `region` not saved to metadata |\n| `test_yaml_format` | `model_dump(exclude_none=True)` excludes empty-string fields, producing no indented nested keys |\n\n---\n\n## Spec Compliance Gaps\n\n### Critical â€” Missing Commands & Modules\n\n| Spec Requirement | Status |\n|---|---|\n| `invoke` command in `main.py` | **MISSING** â€” only `pack`, `build`, `publish` registered |\n| `status` command in `main.py` | **MISSING** |\n| `agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | **MISSING** â€” file doesn't exist |\n| `agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | **MISSING** â€” file doesn't exist |\n| `InvokeRuntime` in `__all__` | **MISSING** â€” `__all__` = `[\"app\", \"PackRuntime\", \"BuildRuntime\", \"PublishRuntime\"]` |\n\n### API Contract Mismatches\n\n| Spec | Implementation | Severity |\n|---|---|---|\n| `version_callback` prints `AgentCube CLI (kubectl agentcube) version: {__version__}` | Prints `agentcube {__version__}` | Medium |\n| `DockerService.remove_image()` returns `bool` | **Method doesn't exist** | Medium |\n| `KubernetesProvider.get_agent_status()` | **Method doesn't exist** | Medium |\n| `KubernetesProvider._sanitize_name()` | **Method doesn't exist** (uses inline `.lower().replace()`) | Low |\n| `KubernetesProvider.delete_agent()` returns `{\"status\": \"deleted\", ...}` | Returns `None` | Medium |\n| `AgentCubeProvider.get_agent_runtime(name, namespace)` | Signature is `get_agent_runtime(name)` â€” no `namespace` param | Low |\n| `publish` command `--provider` help text includes quotes `'agentcube'` / `'k8s'` | No quotes in help text | Trivial |\n\n### Spec-Compliant Items (verified OK)\n\n- Package layout matches design (all listed files present)\n- `pyproject.toml` dependencies, optional deps, console script entry point all match\n- `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model: all fields, validators (language, build_mode, port) match\n- `MetadataOptions` dataclass: all fields and `from_options` match\n- `MetadataService`: load fallback chain (`agent_metadata.yaml` â†’ `agent.yaml` â†’ `metadata.yaml`), save format, `exclude_none=True` all match\n- `PublishRuntime`: provider routing (agentcube/k8s), image preparation, CR deployment, K8s deployment + `wait_for_deployment_ready(timeout=120)` all match\n- `AgentCubeProvider`: CRD group/version/plural, `sessionTimeout`/`maxSessionDuration`, `imagePullSecrets` all match\n- `BuildRuntime`: version increment logic, rollback on failure, local/cloud build routing all match\n- Error handling pattern `_handle_error(e, command_name, verbose)` matches spec\n- Global `--verbose`/`-v` triggers `logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)`\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n**Not fully compliant.** The `publish` command implementation is structurally sound but has 3 metadata update bugs (version/description/region not persisted). More critically, the `invoke` and `status` commands plus their runtime modules are entirely missing, and several service methods (`remove_image`, `get_agent_status`, `delete_agent` return value) don't match the spec.","time":{"start":1775855269367,"end":1775855269367}}}
